{"tid":360601,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"終於打爆左機戰ALPHA3 ,E家開始OGS,有簡中漢化","createTime":"2017-08-15T12:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T16:59:37.000Z","uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0aed76e7891d4f435945ef06a1b18a14fe7d7c9d","tid":360601,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://twpcsx2.blogspot.hk/2012/01/pcsx2-pcsx2-100.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwpcsx2.blogspot.hk%2F2012%2F01%2Fpcsx2-pcsx2-100.html&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8d2c919f\" target=\"_blank\">http://twpcsx2.blogspot.hk/2012/01/pcsx2-pcsx2-100.html</a><br />\n首先響呢度下載模擬器同bios,之後安裝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://game360.ctfile.com/shared/folder_15852846_be3efc44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame360.ctfile.com%2Fshared%2Ffolder_15852846_be3efc44%2F&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ddeadda8\" target=\"_blank\">https://game360.ctfile.com/shared/folder_15852846_be3efc44/</a><br />\n去呢度下載OGS iso<br />\n共兩PART,大約需時7+3小時<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選擇好映像檔之後,如果用KEYBOARD玩設定下D按鍵,之後按快速啟用就玩得,唔識就再睇新手教學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twpcsx2.blogspot.hk/search/label/PCSX2：教學：新手教學\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwpcsx2.blogspot.hk%2Fsearch%2Flabel%2FPCSX2%EF%BC%9A%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=32b8fa2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://twpcsx2.blogspot.hk/search/label/PCSX2：教學：新手教學</a>"},{"pid":"f2a6d3fc637708c7244e81e624b6f60f89e98b74","tid":360601,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"OGS存檔修改方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tzseng.blogspot.hk/2010/08/pcsx2-ps2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftzseng.blogspot.hk%2F2010%2F08%2Fpcsx2-ps2.html&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=49d63e0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://tzseng.blogspot.hk/2010/08/pcsx2-ps2.html</a><br />\n去呢度下載MYMC,將模擬器的存檔由.PS2 EXPORT轉成.PSU<br />\n(OGS有兩個SAVE一個SYSTEM一個GAME,轉細果個即係GAME果個)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.paopaoche.net/psp/74132.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.paopaoche.net%2Fpsp%2F74132.html&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8e6f0ca2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.paopaoche.net/psp/74132.html</a><br />\n下載機戰OGS存檔修改器<br />\n開頭先果個PSU檔,修改<br />\n<br />\n改好之後用MYMC IMPORT返入去<br />\n方法係先按DELETE原本果個GAME SAVE,再IMPORT<br />\n不先DELETE的話會顯示失敗提示 &quot;save file already present&quot;"},{"pid":"9730190d228080c15b323bc938cbe4d5cf795dd6","tid":360601,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://bbs.tgbus.com/thread-6642385-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.tgbus.com%2Fthread-6642385-1-1.html&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9af54d68\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.tgbus.com/thread-6642385-1-1.html</a><br />\n如果開唔到修改器可以用呢個方法(試過兼容模式都無用),我試過係成功<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/zh-TW/download/confirmation.aspx?id=15354\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fdownload%2Fconfirmation.aspx%3Fid%3D15354&d=SyyntnPjcMaXdtaaHlF8%2BQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b40c4c9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/zh-TW/download/confirmation.aspx?id=15354</a><br />\nMicrosoft .NET Framework 2.0 軟體開發套件 (SDK) (x64) <br />\n下載完響安裝路徑SEARCH CorFlags之後COPY去\\Windows\\system32<br />\n再之後照上面條LINK的方法做"},{"pid":"15a5e478236193c971d355e4aafb33d4965bcf0a","tid":360601,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f4a908113342250fa0ecbeb43d6d00db982680","tid":360601,"uid":73043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26